{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_11_03",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 3話 もっともっと最強なんです",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ツアー終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—After the tour ended",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（無事に海外ツアーが終わって、LizNoirは）\n（MV撮影に向けて練習をしているようだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The overseas tour ended safely‚ and LizNoir）\n（seems to be practicing for the music video shoot…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8094138234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……はぁ……ふぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… haa… phew…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.1162132581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（相当激しく追い込んでいるんだな。こころだけ）\n（じゃない、LizNoir全員が疲弊している……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She’s really pushing herself hard… not just Kokoro‚）\n（but all of LizNoir looks exhausted…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……今回のMVのダンス……\n結構、大変かも、ですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… the choreography for this MV…\nIt… might be… pretty tough…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "でもっ！　こんなところでへこたれませんよ～！\nさぁ、もう一回今の動き合わせましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But! Kokoro won’t give up here~!\nAlright‚ let’s sync that move one more time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（めずらしいな、普段のこころだったら「もう疲れた～）\n（莉央さんの鬼ー！」とか言って音を上げるのに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That’s unusual. Normally‚ she’d be whining‚ “I’m tired~）\n（“Rio-san’s a demon~!” or something like that.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、今のワンフレーズ、もうちょっと粘りませんか？\nもっともっと素敵な動きになると思うんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ let’s hold that one phrase a bit longer‚ shall we?\nI think it’ll look even more amazing that way!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら、こころ達はBIG4なんですから～\n愛ちゃんも動いた動いたっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ we’re the BIG4 after all~\nAi-chan‚ move‚ move!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "さぁさぁ～\n次期センターのこころに続いて下さい～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ come on~\nFollow your future center—Kokoro~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（杞憂だったみたいで良かった）\n（本当に……成長したな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Looks like my worries were unfounded. Good.）\n（She’s really… grown.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5304707422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Music Video Shooting Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.8244894188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.9578214805
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.9911548138
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ～～～づがれだ～～～プリン食べた～～い\nでもMV撮影はなんとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aahhh~~~ so tired~~~ I want pudding~~~\nBut somehow‚ I managed to get through the shoot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "間違いなくいいものになるだろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’ll definitely turn out great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.9587275665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.4628147604
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃあっ！？　{user}さん！？\nいつから見てたんですか～？　覗き魔です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hyaa!? {user}-san!?\nHow long have you been watching!? You peeper!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6766.6666667000045,
          "startTime": 97.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "違う、マネージャーだし見守ってただけだ\nSNSに書きこもうとするな、スマホを置いてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I’m your manager. I was just keeping an eye on you.\nDon’t post that on social media. Put your phone down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.9558987461
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、冗談ですよ～。心配してくれたんですよね\n過保護なんですから、も～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu‚ I’m joking~ You were worried about me‚ weren’t you?\nYou’re so overprotective‚ honestly~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、BIG4のこころ達には心配なんてご無用です！\nもっとどっしり構えてて下さい～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But for BIG4 Kokoro‚ worry is unnecessary!\nYou should be more relaxed and confident~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.86541187
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それは心強いな。MVの仕上がりが楽しみだよ\nただ、あまり調子には乗り過ぎないようにな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s reassuring. I’m looking forward to the MV.\nJust don’t get too carried away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "当然じゃないですか～\nこころを誰だと思ってるんですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course~\nWho do you think Kokoro is~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.5430082006
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "本番も楽しみにしていて下さいね～\n絶対いいものにしてみせますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please look forward to the real performance too~\nI’ll make sure it turns out amazing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.4998323443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "楽しみにしてるよ。そうだ、ジュースの差し入れを\n持って来たんだ。良かったら飲んでリラックスしてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m looking forward to it. Oh right‚ I brought some juice.\nHave some and relax‚ if you’d like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4のこころに見合うジュースですか～？\nもっと高級なものを所望します～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it a juice worthy of BIG4’s Kokoro~?\nI demand something fancier~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.8145799322
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "冗談を言える余裕があるみたいで\n安心したよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seems like you’ve still got room to joke.\nThat’s a relief.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.8666575114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "だから過保護ですって～\n大船に乗った気持ちでいて下さいよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you‚ you’re overprotective~\nJust relax and trust me~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.3999908447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.5088834289
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……\nありがとう、こころ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right…\nThanks‚ Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "突然真剣な顔してどうしたんですか～？　まぁこころの\n可愛さに感謝したくなる気持ちは分かりますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s with that serious face all of a sudden~? Well‚ I know\nit’s natural to feel grateful for my cuteness~",
