      "text": "Grab the BIG4で葵が抜けたりして\n大変だったのに諦めずに頑張ってくれただろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Things got tough when Aoi had to step away\nduring \"Grab the BIG4\"‚ but you didn’t give up.",
