      "text": "えへへ、なんだか汗かいてきちゃいましたよ……\nそろそろ本番なのに、どうしてくれるんですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ I’m starting to sweat now…\nThe real shoot’s about to start—what are you gonna do about it~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.8999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
