      "text": "も～、そういう訳じゃないですよ～！\n{user}さん関係なく緊張はしてますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no~ that’s not what I meant!\nI’m nervous regardless of you‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.1999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr023.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になって初めてのMV撮影なんです\nさすがのこころも、それなりに緊張しますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s our first MV shoot as BIG4‚ after all.\nEven Kokoro gets a little nervous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.900004069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……俺に出来ることはあるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… is there anything I can do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.2666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
