      "startTime": 264.8666056314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "お安い御用だ\nちゃんと見守っているよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Consider it done.\nI’ll be watching closely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.8999389647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr026.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんや葵さんがいない時でも\n愛ちゃんもいなくて、たとえ一人の時があったとしても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when Rio-san‚ Aoi-san\nor Ai-chan aren’t around—if I’m ever alone‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 276.8999389647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr027.m4a",
      "text": "こころはLizNoirだって胸を張って言えるように\n自分の足で歩いていけるように、これからも頑張ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to be able to proudly say‚ “I’m LizNoir.”\nI’ll keep working hard so I can stand on my own.",
