      },
      "startTime": 286.2666056314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr028.m4a",
      "text": "お互いに寄りかかっている訳じゃないけれど\nお互いに支え合っている一体感……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re not leaning on each other‚ but\nwe have that sense of mutual support…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 294.633272298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr029.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、今のLizNoirみんなが感じてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure everyone in LizNoir feels that right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 297.8556078278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_03-kkr030.m4a",
      "text": "だからこれまでのリズノワも最強だったけど\nこれからのリズノワはもっともっと最強なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why‚ LizNoir has been the strongest until now‚\nbut LizNoir from now on will be even stronger than ever!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 306.7666056314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
