      "text": "ああ、最強のLizNoirをみんなに見せてやれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ show everyone the strongest LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 311.1861908599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
